  "body": "**What happened**:\r\n\r\nWhen creating an EBS volume, we're currently waiting for the volume be in the correct state before proceeding:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/88ed776c6b447b1882a5fe99df0cfcaba1da4e72/staging/src/k8s.io/legacy-cloud-providers/aws/aws.go#L2398-L2421\r\n\r\nHowever, we're using the interval defined in `encryptedCheckInterval` (e.g., 1 second), which was meant to be used for another reason and might be too soon for this specific case. Also, this might contribute to the API quota being exceeded.\r\n\r\nCC @gnufied @leakingtapan \r\n/sig storage\r\n/sig aws",
